# Specialized Lists and Checklists

## Advanced Checklist with States
- [x] ~~Completed and struck-through task~~
- [ ] Pending task to do
- [~] Task in progress (partial)
- [!] Important/critical task
- [?] Task requiring investigation

## Definition Lists
API
:   Application Programming Interface - Interface for communication between systems

REST
:   Representational State Transfer - Architecture for web services

GraphQL
:   Query language for APIs that allows requesting specific data

JWT
:   JSON Web Token - Standard for transmitting secure information

