# Keyboard and UI Elements

## Key Combinations
To save a file: ++ctrl+s++

To open the developer menu: ++ctrl+shift+i++

On Mac it would be: ++cmd+option+i++

## UI Action Sequences
1. Click ++menu++ → ++file++ → ++new++
2. Press ++tab++ to navigate between fields
3. Use ++enter++ to confirm or ++esc++ to cancel
4. To select all: ++ctrl+a++

