# Technical Documentation Elements

## Code with Line Numbering

```python {1,3-5}
def calculate_fibonacci(n):
    if n <= 1:
        return n
    else:
        return calculate_fibonacci(n-1) + calculate_fibonacci(n-2)

# Usage example
result = calculate_fibonacci(10)
print(f"The tenth Fibonacci number is: {result}")
```

## Code with Specific Highlighting

```javascript {2,7-9}
const apiConfig = {
  baseURL: 'https://api.example.com', // Highlighted line
  timeout: 5000,
  headers: {
    'Content-Type': 'application/json'
  },
  retry: {  // Highlighted block
    attempts: 3,
    delay: 1000
  }
};
```

