# DSL Element Coverage Table

| Element | Syntax | Status | Example |
|----------|----------|--------|---------|
| **Bold** | `**text**` | ✅ Complete | **text** |
| **Italics** | `*text*` | ✅ Complete | *text* |
| **Strikethrough** | `~~text~~` | ✅ Complete | ~~text~~ |
| **Highlight** | `==text==` | ✅ Complete | ==text== |
| **Code** | `` `code` `` | ✅ Complete | `code` |
| **Superscript** | `^text^` | ✅ Complete | ^text^ |
| **Subscript** | `~text~` | ✅ Complete | ~text~ |
| **Math** | `$formula$` | ✅ Complete | $E=mc^2$ |
| **Emojis** | `:emoji:` | ✅ Complete | :smile: |
| **Keyboard** | `++key++` | ✅ Complete | ++ctrl+s++ |
| **References** | `[^note]` | ✅ Complete | [^example] |
| **Abbreviations** | `*[AB]: def` | ✅ Complete | HTML |
| **Checklists** | `- [x]` | ✅ Complete | - [x] ~~Done~~ |
| **Definitions** | `Term\n:   Def` | ✅ Complete | See above |
| **Polls** | `::: poll` | 🚧 Conceptual | See above |

[^example]: This is a sample note.
*[HTML]: HyperText Markup Language

